tall? That would rock. You don\u0027t have to support it, just make the version available. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is now\u00A0fixed on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E. It will show that 1.8 is for 1.2, but that is just some problem we have because its a pre.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MarkusA380","CreatedById":45759,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T16:21:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222773711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022102277\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474819962\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279730\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Olympic1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Olympic1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is now\u00A0fixed on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E. It will show that 1.8 is for 1.2, but that is just some problem we have because its a pre.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, that is great, but I hope you meant 1.8.1! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Olympic1","CreatedById":79730,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T16:24:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222773720\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022102277\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474820519\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002245759\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MarkusA380\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, MarkusA380 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, that is great, but I hope you meant 1.8.1! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant\u00A0that 1.8 will be installed for 1.1.3 now instead of 1.8.1 and 1.8.1 for 1.2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MarkusA380","CreatedById":45759,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T16:25:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222773722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022102277\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474820676\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279730\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Olympic1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Olympic1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant\u00A0that 1.8 will be installed for 1.1.3 now instead of 1.8.1 and 1.8.1 for 1.2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAhhh perrrfect! Thank you very very much!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Friedrich Nietzsche","CreatedById":106208,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-11T10:49:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\njust reporting an issue, that I think, has something to do with persistant rotation: I was tweaking the trajectory of my mars probe and decided to use the \u003Cem\u003Erelative rotation \u003C/em\u003Efeature to keep the probe aligned proper to the sun. After choosing the sun as body in Persistant rotation, the whole screen (except all of\u00A0the menus) turned black. Also the inside of the\u00A0navball dissapeard and only a black area was visible. Short after, ksp crashed with the error on the screenshot. The same happens, if I restart KSP and try to jump to the Mars probe. Jumping to other vessels still works.I\u0027ve attached the error message below:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/KQWuT\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/a/KQWuT\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}